allocate().details: Allocate unallocated funds on Vault to strategies.*

returns._0: uint256 Balance of asset in decimals of asset

claimGovernance().details: Claim Governance of the contract to a new account (`newGovernor`). Can only be called by the new Governor.

getAllStrategies().details: Return the array of all strategies

getStrategyCount().details: Return the number of strategies active on the Vault.

governor().details: Returns the address of the current Governor.

isGovernor().details: Returns true if the caller is the current Governor.

rebase().details: Calculate the total value of assets held by the Vault and all      strategies and update the supply of OETH.

setAdminImpl(address).details: set the implementation for the admin, this needs to be in a base class else we cannot set it

totalValue().details: Determine the total value of assets held by the vault and its         strategies.

transferGovernance(address).details: Transfers Governance of the contract to a new account (`newGovernor`). Can only be called by the current Governor. Must be claimed for this to complete

allocate().notice: Allocate unallocated funds on Vault to strategies.

checkBalance().notice: Get the balance of an asset held in Vault and all strategies.

redeemAll().notice: Withdraw wETH and burn all OETH.
